Ishihara, 
<number box="[385,439,402,424]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" value="1955.0">1955</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
: 
<number box="[449,535,402,424]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" value="215.217">215,217</number>
. Type-species: 
